okay, let me try again... using the 'switch' this time around... lol

(much simplified too)

```
<command name="saying_command">

  <pattern>say #text_parameter# to #object_parameter#</pattern>

  <script>
    saying_function (text_parameter, object_parameter)
  </script>

</command>

